description: Remove tags from a CloudFront resource. For more information, see Tagging a distribution in the Amazon CloudFront Developer Guide.

parameters.name: Resource
parameters.description: An ARN of a CloudFront resource.

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: A complex type that contains zero or more Tag key elements. Items (list) --- A complex type that contains Tag key elements. (string) --- A string that contains Tag key. The string length should be between 1 and 128 characters. Valid characters include a-z, A-Z, 0-9, space, and the special characters _ - . : / = + @.

nested_params.name: Items
nested_params.description: A complex type that contains Tag key elements.
